OL,3,CRising fuel costs - and calls to ease
OL,4,Cthe burden of student loans
OL,6,FTom Sheldrick's guests also consider
OL,7,Fhow we can become more self-sufficient
OL,8,Ffor energy in the medium to long-term
OL,9,F- and help people in rural areas who
OL,10,Fare struggling to pay the rising cost
OL,11,Fof heating oil, because of the war in
OL,12,Fthe Middle East.
OL,14,FConservative peer Lord Kirkhope says a
OL,15,Fprice cap on heating oil is something
OL,16,Fto bear in mind - but stressed the
OL,17,Fimportance of dealing with energy
OL,18,Fcosts longer-term, recommending
OL,19,Fcutting carbon taxes and allowing more
OL,20,Fextraction of North Sea oil and gas.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42103
